data.text: @DubenskyMartyna @Hade_Hdez_4 Right, Martyna. Thanks to the actor and his character, I can escape from everything we are experiencing, more like a dystopian movie or series, than real life. But we already know that, on too many occasions, reality is stranger than fiction.😢
@neuralcluster @DubenskyMartyna Never has a show or actor created so much joy and happiness for so many people in such hard times
